{"tid":613471,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"世界末日","createTime":"2018-04-01T16:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T09:59:19.000Z","uid":41647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"85a4acf2faedb1695d02b5152b71437eb9efc9f3","tid":613471,"uid":41647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T16:47:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NDFULbHgL6E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNDFULbHgL6E&d=HSBRIbRhSvBxCtbBCO%2FyPnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=4c464a11\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NDFULbHgL6E</a><br />\n<br />\n想笑　來偽裝掉下的眼淚　點點頭　承認自己會怕黑<br />\n我只求　能借一點的時間來陪　你卻連同情都不給<br />\n想哭　來試探自己麻痺了沒　全世界　好像只有我疲憊<br />\n無所謂　反正難過就敷衍　走一回　但願絕望和無奈遠走高飛<br />\n<br />\n天灰灰　會不會　讓我忘了你是誰<br />\n夜越黑　夢違背　難追難回味<br />\n我的世界將被摧毀　也許事與願違<br />\n<br />\n累不累　睡不睡　單影無人相依偎<br />\n夜越黑　夢違背　有誰肯安慰<br />\n我的世界將被摧毀　也許頹廢也是另一種美<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562f47b84877ae834dfed2b089a1df2fb061dc4f","tid":613471,"uid":41647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T16:57:47.000Z","msg":"愚人節過後⋯我依然是愚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e72a57c838e4c846b507c487d2a348b2ce86774","tid":613471,"uid":41647,"like":0,"dislike":